#. Tag: glossterm
#: glossary.docbook:30
#, no-c-format
msgid "intuitive highlighting"
msgstr "intuitiv fremhævning"

#. Tag: para
#: glossary.docbook:31
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "This is a feature of &kturtle; that makes coding even easier. With "
#| "intuitive highlighting the code that you write gets a color that "
#| "indicates what type of code it is. In the next list you will find the "
#| "different types of code and the color they get in <link linkend=\"the-"
#| "code-editor\">the code editor</link>."
msgid ""
"This is a feature of &kturtle; that makes coding even easier. With intuitive "
"highlighting the code that you write gets a color that indicates what type "
"of code it is. In the next list you will find the different types of code "
"and the color they get in <link linkend=\"the-editor\">the editor</link>."
msgstr ""
"Dette er en funktion af &kturtle; der gør kodning endnu nemmere. Med "
"intuitiv fremhævning får koden du skriver en farve der indikerer hvilken "
"type kode det er. I den næste liste vil du finde de forskellige typer kode "
"og den farve de får i <link linkend=\"the-code-editor\">kodeeditoren</link>."

